Open-source Superintelligence

Usage: soma <COMMAND>

Commands:
  balance          Check SOMA balance for an address
  transfer         Transfer SOMA or USDC to one or more recipients
  transfer-object  Transfer an object to a recipient
  stake            Stake SOMA with a validator
  unstake          Withdraw staked SOMA
  merge            Merge dust coins to reduce object count [aliases: merge-coins]
  status           Show network connection status, version info, and active address
  objects          Query on-chain objects by owner or ID
  tx               Get transaction details or execute serialized transactions
  wallet           Manage wallet addresses and keys
  env              Manage network environments (switch, add, list)
  validator        Manage validators (register, set gas price, commission)
  start            Start a long-running service (localnet, validator)
  network          Inspect local network configuration and validator addresses
  genesis          Bootstrap and initialize a new SOMA network
  keytool          Low-level keystore operations (generate, import, export keys)
  help             Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
